title: Spittin' Chiclets Episode 108: Featuring Jack Eichel, Noah Hanifin, And Oliver Ekman-Larsson
description:
On this first Monday episode of the season, the guys are joined by a star studded, very rich group of NHL hockey players. First, the new captain of the Arizona Coyotes, Oliver Ekman-Larsson joined the podcast to talk about his career and the upcoming year, as well as living with Biz last season. The boys then do a Pacific division preview, breaking down every team in the division and then wrap up with a great interview with Jack Eichel and Noah Hanifin.


You can find every episode of this show on Apple Podcasts, Spotify or YouTube. Prime Members can listen ad-free on Amazon Music. For more, visit barstool.link/schiclets
